channel.description:
Well, I just had a two hour conversation with Davidi2 about Packets, Bytes & Networking.
He logged our conversation (thank god, cause I'll barely remember this in the morning), and I'd like to share it with all of you.
Some of you may think this is ridiculous, but it may be able to benefit you.
Netorking.txt, 47.9 KB: http://www.mediafire.com/?luoqm758usxh78m
